# 🤖 AI Knowledge Base Assistant

An AI-powered Knowledge Base Assistant built using **n8n**, **Google Gemini**, and **Retrieval-Augmented Generation (RAG)**.

This project automatically collects Question & Answer submissions through a form, enriches them using AI-generated tags, stores them in a searchable knowledge base, and enables users to ask intelligent questions using a RAG-powered AI Assistant.

---

# 📸 Workflow Overview

> Complete n8n workflow of the AI Knowledge Base Assistant.

![Workflow Overview](assets/workflow-overview.png)

---

# 🚀 Features

- 📋 Public Question & Answer Submission Form
- ✅ Email Validation
- 🤖 AI-generated Tags using Google Gemini
- 🗄️ Automatic Storage in n8n Data Tables
- 🔍 Retrieval-Augmented Generation (RAG)
- 💬 AI Chat Assistant
- 🧠 Conversation Memory
- ⚡ Fully Automated using n8n
- 🔄 No Custom Backend Required

---

# 📝 Form Submission Workflow

The submission workflow validates user inputs, generates AI-powered tags using Google Gemini, and stores structured data inside the Knowledge Base.

![Form Submission Workflow](assets/form-submission-workflow.png)

---

# 🤖 RAG Chat Workflow

The AI Assistant retrieves relevant knowledge from the database and generates accurate responses using Retrieval-Augmented Generation (RAG).

![RAG Chat Workflow](assets/rag-chat-workflow.png)

---

# 🏗️ Project Architecture

```text
                User
                  │
                  ▼
        Q&A Submission Form
                  │
                  ▼
          Email Validation
                  │
                  ▼
      Google Gemini (AI Tag Generation)
                  │
                  ▼
      n8n Data Table (Knowledge Base)
                  │
                  ▼
        AI Agent (RAG Retrieval)
                  │
                  ▼
          AI Chat Assistant
```

